{"type":"message","id":"72b62b7b","parentId":"eb60edfa","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:36:36.748Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-01 16:36:36 GMT+8] Exec completed (good-cov, code 0) :: -> 08:07.000] 这样以后,你的决定就清晰从容了。 [08:07.000 --> 08:20.000] 从一多年经历过无数家庭的生离死别悲欢故事,我算是盘明白了点道理,人这一生啊,富贵是算不准的,但幸福是可以算的, [08:20.000 --> 08:29.000] 姻缘是算不准的,但家庭和睦是可以算的,生死是算不准的,但健康是可以算的。 [08…\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Wednesday, April 1st, 2026 — 4:36 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-01 08:36 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775032596745}}
