{"type":"message","id":"545fe176","parentId":"05c3a018","timestamp":"2026-04-01T09:06:03.754Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ **Whisper 转录技能创建完成！**\n\n技能目录结构：\n\n```\nskills/whisper-transcribe/\n├── SKILL.md          # 技能说明（OpenClaw 读取）\n├── README.md         # 项目说明\n├── package.json      # AgentSkills 规范\n└── scripts/\n    └── transcribe.sh # 可执行脚本\n```\n\n## 使用方式\n\n以后当用户需要提取音视频文本时，OpenClaw 会自动匹配这个技能：\n\n**触发场景：**\n- \"帮我把这个 MP3 转成文字\"\n- \"提取这个视频的字幕\"\n- \"用 whisper 转录音频\"\n- \"生成带时间戳的字幕\"\n\n**参数说明：**\n- `input_file`: 输入文件路径（必填）\n- `output_format`: 输出格式，可选 `txt/vtt/srt/all`，默认 `all`\n- `language`: 语言代码，中文 `zh`，英文 `en`，默认自动检测\n- `model`: 模型大小，`tiny/base/small/medium/large`，默认 `medium`（中文推荐）\n\n**使用示例：**\n```bash\n# 使用脚本\n./skills/whisper-transcribe/scripts/transcribe.sh audio.mp3 vtt zh medium\n\n# 或者直接调用 whisper\nwhisper audio.mp3 --model medium --language zh --output_format vtt\n```\n\n现在这个技能已经创建好了，下次需要提取音视频文本时就可以直接用啦！🎉"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":907,"output":333,"cacheRead":27960,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29200,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775034344528,"responseId":"02177503434467337079cdcc08b35ab782b1fd6e8da4cf042db67"}}
